trans-unit.source: Represents a directory object in a virtual file or resource space.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en mappe objekt i et virtuelt område fil eller ressurs.

trans-unit.source: The VirtualDirectory class is the base class for objects that represent directories in a virtual file system.
trans-unit.target: Klassen VirtualDirectory er basisklasse for objekter som representerer mapper i en virtuell filsystemet.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you would implement a descendent of the VirtualDirectory class for each <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathProvider> class descendent in your Web application.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis du vil implementere en etterkommer av klassen VirtualDirectory for hver <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathProvider>klassen etterfølger i webprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathProvider>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The virtual path to the resource represented by this instance.
trans-unit.target: Den virtuelle banen til ressursen som er representert i denne forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of the files and subdirectories contained in this virtual directory.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste over filer og undermapper i den virtuelle mappen.

trans-unit.source: The Children property contains both <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> and <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects that represent the files and directories contained in this virtual directory.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen underordnede inneholder både <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>og <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objekter som representerer filer og mapper i denne virtuelle mappen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: To return only the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> objects, use the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Files%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer bare den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>objektene, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Files%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Files%2A> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: To return only the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects, use the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Directories%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer bare den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objektene, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Directories%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Directories%2A> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface containing <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnitt som inneholder <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"> </xref> objekter.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of all the subdirectories contained in this directory.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste over alle undermapper i denne mappen.

trans-unit.source: The Directories property contains <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects that represent the directories contained in this virtual directory.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen mapper inneholder <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objekter som representerer mapper i denne virtuelle mappen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>

trans-unit.source: To return the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> objects, use the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Files%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>objektene, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Files%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Files%2A> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: To return both <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> and <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects, use the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Children%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer både <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>og <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objektene, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Children%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Children%2A> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface containing <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnitt som inneholder <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"> </xref> objekter.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of all files contained in this directory.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste over alle filene i denne mappen.

trans-unit.source: The Files property contains <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> objects that represent the files contained in this virtual directory.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen filer inneholder <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>objekter som representerer filene i denne virtuelle mappen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: To return the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects, use the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Directories%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objektene, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Directories%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Directories%2A> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>

trans-unit.source: To return both <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> and <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects, use the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Children%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer både <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>og <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objektene, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Children%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory.Children%2A> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface containing <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnitt som inneholder <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile"> </xref> objekter.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates that this is a virtual resource that should be treated as a directory.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir at dette er en virtuell ressurs som skal behandles som en mappe.
